*Download and Install Fonts*
Download fonts from https://github.com/downloads/aravindavk/Gubbi/Gubbi-1.3.zip
    
*Linux Users*
1. Unzip and copy Gubbi.ttf to $HOME/.fonts directory.
2. Run fc-cache in Terminal

*Windows Users*
1. Unzip the downloaded Font zip. 
2. Right click and select Install font option

*For Package maintainers*
Source package: https://github.com/downloads/aravindavk/Gubbi/gubbi-source-1.3.tar.xz
Binary package: https://github.com/downloads/aravindavk/Gubbi/gubbi-ttf-1.3.tar.xz
    
*Any issues?* 
Send mail to root AT aravindavk.in  or Open an issue https://github.com/aravindavk/Gubbi/issues/new (Requires github login)
